OL,7,FAn American sports team owned by
OL,8,FManchester United owners the Glazers
OL,9,Fhas "smelly facilities" and bug
OL,10,Fproblems, a new report has detailed.
OL,12,FPlayers for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers,
OL,13,Fwho play in the NFL, gave club owner
OL,14,FJoel Glazer 6.1/10 for his
OL,15,F"willingness to invest in the
OL,16,Ffacilities" in a nation-wide survey.
