OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe review, aiming to highlight the
OL,8,Fworking conditions for players across
OL,9,Fthe league, was published by the
OL,10,FNational Football League Player
OL,11,FAssociation (NFLPA) in America.
OL,13,FManchester United supporters have
OL,14,Fconsistently protested against the
OL,15,FGlazers ownership since their majority
OL,16,Ftakeover in 2005, particularly the
OL,17,Flack of investment on Old Trafford and
OL,18,Fthe Carrington training ground.
