OL,7,FIssues listed by Tampa Bay players
OL,8,Fincluded constantly smelling and
OL,9,Funclean facilities, and a "persistent
OL,10,Fbug issue" in the area where the team
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,13,FIt was revealed the sauna which is
OL,14,Fdirty and mouldy, consistently breaks
OL,15,Fdown.
OL,17,FThe NFL team also ranked 22nd on
OL,18,Faspects of the 'locker room'.
