OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe report ranked the Glazers's NFL
OL,8,Fownership 29th out 32 clubs across the
OL,9,Fleague.
OL,11,FThe also report analysed categories
OL,12,Fsuch as food, training staff, team
OL,13,Ftravel and the treatment of families.
OL,15,FIn the club's report card, the NFLPA
OL,16,Fsaid: "The Tampa Bay Buccaneers finish
OL,17,Fthe year ranked 24th overall; the
OL,18,Franking could have been lower if the
OL,19,Fstaff had not earned high marks among
OL,20,Frespondents.
