OL,3,CThe Glazers criticised for the lack of
OL,4,Cinvestment in their American sports
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"The dietician, training staff and
OL,8,Fstrength coaches all received solid
OL,9,Fgrades from the players.
OL,11,F"Club owner Joel Glazer ranks 29th
OL,12,Facross the league when it comes to the
OL,13,Fquestion about a perceived willingness
OL,14,Fto invest in the facilities, and the
OL,15,Freason for assessment is reflected in
OL,16,Fthe data collected across categories.
OL,18,F"The players described the locker room
OL,19,Fas "unclean" and "smelly," and they
OL,20,Feven cited seeing bugs consistently in
OL,21,Fthe showers.
