OL,3,CThe Glazers criticised for the lack of
OL,4,Cinvestment in their American sports
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"Respondents also described the team
OL,8,Fsauna as 'dirty,' 'small' and 'broken
OL,9,Fdown'.
OL,11,F"Younger players must have roommates
OL,12,Fon work travel, unless they pay the
OL,13,Fteam more than $1,750 for their own
OL,14,Froom each season.
OL,16,F"They do have a daycare room on
OL,17,Fgamedays, but charge players' families
OL,18,F$90 per child, which most other teams
OL,19,Foffer for free.
