OL,3,CThe Glazers criticised for the lack of
OL,4,Cinvestment in their American sports
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"Outdated facilities are one thing,
OL,8,Fbut providing clean showers and
OL,9,Fworkspaces, and not charging players
OL,10,Fto have their own hotel room on work
OL,11,Ftrips should be basic standards for a
OL,12,Fmulti-billion-dollar professional
OL,13,Fsports enterprise."
OL,15,FIn a statement responding to the
OL,16,Freport, Tampa Bay Buccaneers said: "We
OL,17,Fvalue the NFLPA report and the input
OL,18,Ffrom our players that it provides.
